{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21424793cf","title":"任传耕“病情诊断书”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"45f0422c18","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":18,"articleId":"21424793cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"279bf221e7","name":"叶宗荫/翟富春"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bc8c323e72","type":"title","text":"任传耕“病情诊断书”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"1708b6ae39","type":"authors","text":"叶宗荫/翟富春","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"fde77b581d","type":"paragraph","text":"姓名  任传耕","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"f2c98e873e","type":"paragraph","text":"性别  男","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"be884aa8ed","type":"paragraph","text":"年龄  三十二岁","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"3c036fbe56","type":"paragraph","text":"病历  大鸣大放期间，病人过度兴奋，潜伏已久的反党反社会主义的狂热病大发。他说党的政策不能代表人民的利益；他主张取消团组织；他认为我国过分地刺激了美帝国主义，使中美关系搞不好，并认为这是我国外交上的失败；他要求政府释放他过去欺压人民、作恶多端的父亲和岳父；他欢迎蒋介石重新回到大陆；他想偷越国境逃往台湾或美国，为蒋介石和美帝国主义效劳。群众曾耐心地为他治病，但本人执迷不悟，故病情日重，发展下去，势将自绝于人民。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"e603fa27a5","type":"paragraph","text":"病人反对过“土改”，在镇反时袒护过反革命分子，在反对美帝侵略朝鲜的战争时期患过严重的“恐美病”，在肃反中作假检讨，企图蒙混过关……","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"a9f12a7198","type":"paragraph","text":"病人生于地主官僚家庭，其父为蒋介石军队的炮兵上校，叔父为三青团头目，岳父为军统特务，本人解放前参加过三青团，向往“西方文明”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"05f21ae858","type":"paragraph","text":"体格检查  两眼有黑内障；两耳充满“右派耵聍”重听；满口臭气；心脏向“右”转位；腹内美国之音亢进；臀部坐骨脱节处有“官僚资产阶级立场”；大脑为“反动型”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"c1edea3582","type":"paragraph","text":"诊断  反党、反人民、反社会主义“狂”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"bcc55512b1","type":"paragraph","text":"治疗方案","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"d95a4827e1","type":"paragraph","text":"１．内服脱胎换骨丹，改变反动神经型。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"ef4ccbc077","type":"paragraph","text":"２．心脏向左位整复术，以面向人民。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"98d45de172","type":"paragraph","text":"３．“黑内障”及“右派耵聍”扎出术，以接受事实教育。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"0f83020cb4","type":"paragraph","text":"４．禁忌坚持反动立场及假检讨。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"},{"id":"21317b3277","type":"paragraph","text":" ——原载《解放军报》1957年7月18日","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf"}],"page":{"id":"c3bd84b8a1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"21424793cf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}